OL,3,CIllegal dog breeders sentenced after
OL,4,C'dead body smell' alerts neighbours
OL,6,FIllegal breeders in Cardiff ran a
OL,7,F"putrid" puppy farm that left police
OL,8,Fofficers "physically sick" from the
OL,9,Fsmell with dozens of dogs kept in
OL,10,Finhumane conditions.
OL,12,FTuran Kiran, 48, and Cetin Kiral, 34,
OL,13,Fwere sentenced on January 21 following
OL,14,Freports of the smell of a "dead body"
OL,15,Fcoming from a property, Cardiff
OL,16,FCouncil says.
