OL,3,CIllegal dog breeders sentenced after
OL,4,C'dead body smell' alerts neighbours
OL,6,FWhen officers attended, they found 38
OL,7,Fdogs living in extremely poor
OL,8,Fconditions, with a strong smell of
OL,9,Furine and faeces throughout the
OL,10,Fpremises.
OL,12,FKiran initially claimed that only 20
OL,13,Fdogs were at the property but admitted
OL,14,Fhe did not hold a dog breeders'
OL,15,Flicence.
OL,17,FThe property was unfit for both human
OL,18,Fand animal habitation, and 17 of the
OL,19,Fdogs were found to be suffering and in
OL,20,Fpain.
