OL,6,FKiran pleaded guilty to 17 counts of
OL,7,Fcausing unnecessary suffering to a
OL,8,Fprotected animal. Kiral pleaded guilty
OL,9,Fto one count of causing unnecessary
OL,10,Fsuffering to a protected animal.
OL,12,FKiran received an 18week prison
OL,13,Fsentence, suspended for 12 months, and
OL,14,Fwas ordered to complete 20 days of
OL,15,Frehabilitation activity and 150 hours
OL,16,Fof unpaid work.
