OL,6,FCllr Norma Mackie, Cabinet Member
OL,7,Fresponsible for Shared Regulatory
OL,8,FServices at Cardiff Council, said:
OL,9,F"The stench coming from this property
OL,10,Falerted authorities to the crimes that
OL,11,Fwere taking placed inside, and what
OL,12,Fofficers uncovered was a putrid puppy
OL,13,Ffarm that left police and council
OL,14,Fofficers physically sick from the
OL,15,Fsmell. The suffering these animals
OL,16,Fendured was clear, and the lifetime
OL,17,Fban means these individuals can never
OL,18,Flegally breed dogs again.
