OL,6,FVeterinary examinations found multiple
OL,7,Funtreated infections affecting the
OL,8,Fdogs' eyes, ears, skin, and general
OL,9,Fhealth. Seven dogs were seized under
OL,10,Fthe Animal Welfare Act due to the
OL,11,Fseverity of their condition.
