OL,6,FA review of veterinary records,
OL,7,Fbreeding paperwork, social media
OL,8,Factivity, and microchip data revealed
OL,9,Fthat Boston had bred large numbers of
OL,10,Flitters without a licence, in breach
OL,11,Fof the Animal Welfare Act, Cardiff
OL,12,FCouncil say. Some dogs had been
OL,13,Foverbred, including one that gave
OL,14,Fbirth only months after a vet
OL,15,Finstructed that no further breeding
OL,16,Fshould take place. No import documents
OL,17,For passports were found for any of the
OL,18,Fdogs, despite all having cropped ears.
